               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; incipits and headings of the texts; the words መፍቀሬ፡ አምላክ፡ standing for the name of the reigning monarch; directives for the ministers (e.g., fol. 51vb); names of the patriarch and metropolitan; names of the donors mentioned at the beginning of the Anaphoras; names of the Evangelists (e.g., fols. 86v-87r); the words ቡራኬ፡, ዕማሬ፡ (እማሬ፡), በእንተ፡, ወእምዝ፡; the word ርኁቀ፡ in: ይበል፡ ቀሲስ፡ … በለኈሳስ፡ ርኁቀ፡ (e.g., fol.84vb, l.12); abbreviations; elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals; some of the corrections written above or beside the words (e.g., fols. 8vb, 9ra).</rubric>
                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="coloph1">
                     <colophon>
                        <locus target="124ra"/>Fol. 124ra: ዝ፡ ቅዳሴ፡ ዘሰሀስሕለ፡ ቂርቆስ፡ ዘተጽሕፈ፡ በንዋዩ፡ ዘጸሐፎ፡ &lt;...&gt;እም፡ አመ፡ ጸአቱ፡ ብሔረ፡ ኢትዮጵያ፡ ለጳጳስ፡ አቡነ፡ ሰላማ፡ ዳግማዊ፡ በ፳ወ፪፡ ዓመት፡ ወመንፈቀ፡ ዓመት፡ እም፡ አመ፡ ነግሠ፡ ንጉሠ፡ ነገሥት፡ ቴዎድሮስ፡ በ፲ወ፪፡ ዓመት፡ ዘሰረቆ፡ ወዘፈሀቆ፡ ውጉዘ፡ ይኩን፡ በሦልጣነ[sic]፡ ጴጥሮስ፡ ወጳውሎስ፨<foreign xml:lang="en">Fol. 124ra: This Missal is of Sahasǝḥlä Qirqos, which was written with its own money; the one who wrote it is &lt;...&gt;, in the 22th year and a half after the arrival of the bishop ʾabunä Sälama II in the land of Ethiopia, and 12 after the enthronement of the King of Kings Tewodros. He who steals it or erases [its text] shall be excommunicated by the authority of Peter and Paul.
</foreign>
                        <note>The name of the scribe has been effaced.</note>
                     </colophon>
                  </msItem>
